</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="附加区域-aside" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#附加区域-aside" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 附加区域 aside</h2>
<p>使用 <code v-pre>aside</code> 用于设置与主要区域无关的内容，比如侧面栏的广告等。</p>
<div class="language-html ext-html line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-html"><code><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>body</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>main</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
